  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The Efficacy of HMPL 004 Given at 1200 mg/Day, Assessed After 8 Weeks of Treatment With HMPL-004 in Inducing a Drop in the Subject's Crohn's Disease Activity Index (CDAI) by 100 Points.</measure>
    <time_frame>8 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>For the Intention to Treat (ITT) population, the Worst Observation Carried Forward (WOCF) method, was used to measure the percentage of subjects in the HMPL 004 group as compared to the placebo group that achieved a clinical response of a CDAI reduction of 100 points at Week 8 as compared to the subject's entry level CDAI score.</description>
